title: Teemo Fan Art

embed.description: Website | Facebook [Add Me!] Little fan art I did of Teemo, the character I most like to play to annoy the crap out of everyone else. League of Legends: Teemo Splashscreen

body:
Hey Everyone, 

Wanted to do a fan art for a splash screen type illustration. Chose Teemo because thats the char I play the most. So much fun annoying people :D:D

Let me know what you think!

replies.body:
If you ever meet this person. Report them for using Teemo.

(joking)

Teemo... My mortal enemy
